670
00:39:15,640 --> 00:39:18,520
You're putting your family in danger
just because you're passionate

671
00:39:18,520 --> 00:39:21,040
about re-opening the case.

672
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:24,760
I didn't think that much.

673
00:39:24,760 --> 00:39:26,160
I apologize.

674
00:39:26,160 --> 00:39:27,200
Anyway,

675
00:39:27,200 --> 00:39:30,240
