676
00:39:30,240 --> 00:39:31,560
And I will send someone

677
00:39:31,560 --> 00:39:33,920
to look after your parents.

678
00:39:35,680 --> 00:39:37,840
We will work on the case.

679
00:39:37,840 --> 00:39:40,360
Before the truth comes out,

680
00:39:40,360 --> 00:39:42,480
